description:
Available September 1st. Nicely renovated 1 bed / 1 bath condo located just off D Street in South Boston. Within walking distance to both Andrew Square and Broadway T Stations.

This condo features hardwood floors throughout, an open-concept kitchen with stainless steel appliances and a breakfast bar, a spacious bedroom with ample closet space, a private rear deck, and a recently renovated bathroom.

Renter is responsible for gas heating.
One year lease required.
Credit check and reference required.
